{"tid":609602,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] Mitrasphere (XX) 撚都唔信而家無人玩","createTime":"2018-03-29T07:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T07:27:54.000Z","uid":129852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3e45dc8277c942fcb7617470b160beee86d3f493","tid":609602,"uid":129852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新手唔好怕麻煩 唔該睇睇</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://gamewith.akamaized.net/service/hd/images/426689515fe6db51c8d8b1b6a93852f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.akamaized.net%2Fservice%2Fhd%2Fimages%2F426689515fe6db51c8d8b1b6a93852f7.png&h=5e3c4d07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日文名: ミトラスフィア<br />\n<br />\n大量聲優坐陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://gamewith.akamaized.net/img/b20dead2abeac8b7dd7487aa5999fbc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.akamaized.net%2Fimg%2Fb20dead2abeac8b7dd7487aa5999fbc4.jpg&h=ff6d3acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gamewith.akamaized.net/service/hd/images/4c781f37bd665ef36feacb7b7fd3b832.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.akamaized.net%2Fservice%2Fhd%2Fimages%2F4c781f37bd665ef36feacb7b7fd3b832.jpg&h=11350770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男女聲優合共20幾位慢慢J<br />\n連龍珠婆婆都有參與其中<br />\n<br />\n回合制, 自定造型, 每職業8種武器 加 5防具<br />\n<img src=\"https://gamewith.akamaized.net/img/8b1740b6bd26cdd0769a2c24c3c1e9c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.akamaized.net%2Fimg%2F8b1740b6bd26cdd0769a2c24c3c1e9c3.jpg&h=e904e804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大量動作同叫聲可以係地圖亂用<br />\n<img src=\"https://gamewith.akamaized.net/img/b28cc26b52bfa05445393dd236e7a016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.akamaized.net%2Fimg%2Fb28cc26b52bfa05445393dd236e7a016.jpg&h=48b3197e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5種職業<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.img-conv.gamerch.com/img.gamerch.com/mitrasphere/1486109666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.img-conv.gamerch.com%2Fimg.gamerch.com%2Fmitrasphere%2F1486109666.jpg&h=ec9f4a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劍術士: 單體物理最強<br />\n護術士: 坦得落BUFF又可自己補自己<br />\n聖導士: 補師冇咩好講啦, 最緊要有得蘇生<br />\n弓術士: 群攻技, 支援, 大大力BUFF<br />\n魔導士: 大大力魔師, 群技<br />\n<br />\n介紹片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WYsjX75WHAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWYsjX75WHAQ&d=WtV8rLE4pArhkj3eEZDXmUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=3d99a652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WYsjX75WHAQ</a>"},{"pid":"b81200976d93090e604d7933c38c5f33e24227fd","tid":609602,"uid":129852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:22:40.000Z","msg":"[quote]<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Q&amp;A</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q:首抽抽咩好, 點抽好?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 評價網 - <br />\n<a href=\"https://altema.jp/mitrasphere/bukilist?rea%5B%5D=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faltema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbukilist%3Frea%255B%255D%3D4&d=WtV8rLE4pArhkj3eEZDXmUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=6ac601bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://altema.jp/mitrasphere/bukilist?rea%5B%5D=4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://altema.jp/mitrasphere/risemara\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faltema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Frisemara&d=WtV8rLE4pArhkj3eEZDXmUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7b84fde6\" target=\"_blank\">https://altema.jp/mitrasphere/risemara</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8月14號開始, 一開波送石夠你70連 <strong>(4星機率 10%) 暫時4星最頂, 冇5星</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nStep1 -\t免費10連, 魔具嚟, 咩職都用得 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/237.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F237.jpg&h=e84d64f3&s={SIZE}\" />劍/魔最好有呢舊野 <span style=\"color: red;\">下一擊100%爆擊</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F249.jpg&h=99a61b08&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F213.jpg&h=42f1428f&s={SIZE}\" />坦就呢舊 群體吸仇恨 / 回血<br />\n<br />\nStep2 -\t250石10連保底1件4*武: (同光武POOL一樣,但光POOL冇保底) <br />\n\t抽全職武器果個POOL, 如果玩死一職, 最好一下就抽中自己職煌武<br />\n<br />\nStep3 -\t250石10連保底1件4*武:<br />\n\t當你抽完全職POOL, 抽到你想要嘅武, 就ALL IN職業限定POOL 到你抽到理想為止<br />\n<br />\nStep4 - 水pool 每日1石10連<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>or</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好煩 All in 自己職, 一樣有機會出煌武, 靚就開, 唔識就睇#3, 覺得自己好蠢 睇極都唔識先問人啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 又係ON9要突武game, 玩嚟做乜?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 每把武可以突5次, 4星食2,3(20%)星都得, 絕對唔似其他game 咁on9要焗你食相同星<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 有冇PVP 同公會?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 冇, 共鬥為主, 可以開房組隊一齊打任, 或者抱課長大腿farm裝過關<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 除左抽仲點拎其他裝?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 打主線, 活動, 會送4星勁裝 (現時建議谷戰力打活動狼王, 獎品豐富, 包括4星防具 突滿會係現時最強防具 - 數值偏向物魔防, 想魔攻高不適用)<br />\n遲下仲有更多時裝活動, 大量時裝俾你改造型<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 武器係咪要升技嫁?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 要, 但唔洗抽相同武, 可以分解冇用武黎升技 <br />\nPS: 抽到最勁果把野記得放第一個武器位, 因為主線會有得免費升技1次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 一開波係劍士, 係咪可以轉職?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 可以隨時轉, 想玩咩就玩咩, 唔洗升技升能力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 造型係咪SET死?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 唔係, 可以隨時更改配搭, 幫囡囡換衫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 一開GAME要揀男女同改名, 之後有冇得改先?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 可以, 男女24小時換1次<br />\n名可以重用,但要改就要課金石(100)先改到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 造型好似唔係幾夠洗喎?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 唔止, 隻game有探索功能, 每1個鐘探1次, 最多儲5次, 執地圖閃閃下嘅(可以用石加上限或回滿)<br />\n探索可以拎到唔同嘅珍珠去換石,強化資源,勁裝,同埋頭髮造型<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GwoW7i1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGwoW7i1.jpg&h=481ca144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖為取自kekeke某位人兄嘅探索結果, 魔具能力 - 魔攻特大UP<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/082432_6f46a20848275838b51556edfb8f4ae4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F082432_6f46a20848275838b51556edfb8f4ae4.jpg&h=4874e803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 講左咁耐, 點引繼呀?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 請注意 ios同an 互轉可能會冇晒免費石 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/204940_c1292010a4198004614c9b19589715d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F204940_c1292010a4198004614c9b19589715d1.jpg&h=e9930cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/204941_5e056194f3ceec2dda3575e5b3af3271.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F204941_5e056194f3ceec2dda3575e5b3af3271.jpg&h=d67bbd6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/204942_1679be55d6c27697ed124180294ce673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F204942_1679be55d6c27697ed124180294ce673.jpg&h=c3509645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片由 darksze巴打提供<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 強化關點入呀??</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong>強化關卡時間表 <span style=\"color: red;\">紅豆 - 武器專用</span><br />\n每場最高22xx粒豆 打足一粒鐘約10幾萬<br />\n（）內時間是日本時間，（）外時間是台灣/香港時間<br />\n請注意必須要轉日本時間<br />\n請注意必須要轉日本時間<br />\n請注意必須要轉日本時間<br />\n所以說3次<br />\n<br />\n時段以下：<br />\n<br />\n第一段時間06:00am(07:00am)<br />\n第二段時間11:00am(12:00pm)<br />\n第三段時間07:00pm(08:00pm)<br />\n第四段時間09:30pm(10:30pm）<br />\n<br />\n如果沒轉日本時間遊戲內6:00am,11:00am,07:00pm,09:30pm不會有強化關卡出現，但會7:00am,12:00pm,08:00pm,10:30pm出現但進入關卡時會說關卡已經完結<br />\nFrom baha<br />\n鳴謝 烏蛟騰巴打<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍豆 - 防具專用</span><br />\n曜日上級每場約1000粒左右<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠豆 - 裝飾專用</span><br />\n故事地圖 見到有共闘100%就入去打, 付場每人送你100粒豆, 共400左右<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 有冇3星勁防具?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/082430_7d75fb5c936486ad6ba1020e12696221.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F082430_7d75fb5c936486ad6ba1020e12696221.jpg&h=b58ba401&s={SIZE}\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"83d0cc4e702ac9cde84d2c27dd54d5369e4df1e9","tid":609602,"uid":129852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:22:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">職業防具請係自己職業POOL 抽先最易</span></span></strong><br />\n坦必要裝備:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F2.jpg&h=a6935e05&s={SIZE}\" />配龍人回升, 全隊物傷少30% 可連50%果把一齊使用 最多減少80%物傷, 60%魔傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F73.jpg&h=02ca42b9&s={SIZE}\" />被回復多20%, 80%血以上傷害2倍, 配煌武出自補一流<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F53.jpg&h=2c3c6a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F69.jpg&h=84714a32&s={SIZE}\" />吸仇恨 +5000果把優先 其次800% 暫時是但一把都夠 2把有齊最穩定<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F77.jpg&h=86804c43&s={SIZE}\" />BUFF攻30%  攻大 唔錯選擇 物理扣多30% 用前注意<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F61.jpg&h=57945187&s={SIZE}\" />物魔傷-50% 好重要<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F213.jpg&h=42f1428f&s={SIZE}\" />回自己血(極大) 多一重保護, 一流<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>各位玩坦嘅朋友, 請捉緊時間打齊活動狼BOSS套裝(最好突滿埋啦,多餘嘅用黎分解升技) HP特大UP, 比職業防具(物防特大UP)易有, 突滿數值更勁</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n補必要裝備:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F4.jpg&h=60fc5782&s={SIZE}\" />全隊補血加低機率蘇生 (龍人時100%蘇生)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/109.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F109.jpg&h=2f7df107&s={SIZE}\" />單補同蘇生, 有1-2把就好<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F113.jpg&h=a9c6f98c&s={SIZE}\" />唯一大大力全體傷害, 有把就最好啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F105.jpg&h=78d2e448&s={SIZE}\" />回復力UP 補血更穩定<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F97.jpg&h=4e4297d1&s={SIZE}\" />全補, 有1,2把就可以輕鬆好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/uploads/2017/06/2017y07m05d_195956713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F2017y07m05d_195956713.jpg&h=e2c6a07d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/uploads/2017/06/2017y07m05d_200019838.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F2017y07m05d_200019838.jpg&h=ac23c781&s={SIZE}\" />補套  回復力特大up <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好難抽 唔好勉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n魔必要裝備<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F5.jpg&h=ac56571c&s={SIZE}\" />出招好型 全體特大傷再加10%攻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/181.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F181.jpg&h=474048aa&s={SIZE}\" />全體大傷&amp;20%魔傷up 有2把就正(光+水), 個人認為3把全體傷已經夠皮<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/177.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F177.jpg&h=5e968efc&s={SIZE}\" />龍人量大提升 1-2把 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F185.jpg&h=c30a4650&s={SIZE}\" />單體特大傷仲要回血 2把最好啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F169.jpg&h=5c67888d&s={SIZE}\" />提升30%魔傷 25秒 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/uploads/2017/06/2017y07m03d_134518195.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F2017y07m03d_134518195.jpg&h=3e794554&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/uploads/2017/06/2017y07m03d_150426749.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F2017y07m03d_150426749.jpg&h=56afbc91&s={SIZE}\" />每件魔攻特大 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好難抽 唔好勉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由於太多人問劍職冇咩人理 我就出埋俾你地參考啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F1.jpg&h=281c59e6&s={SIZE}\" />極大攻 比特大更大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F17.jpg&h=f59a35c9&s={SIZE}\" />特大攻 最正有2把<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F25.jpg&h=8e320e71&s={SIZE}\" />攻少 但下一擊多200%傷 迅間傷害爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span style=\"color: red;\">背水劍 使用後受傷害量多25%</span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F33.jpg&h=5f2613b5&s={SIZE}\" />當擊中, 敵被物理扣多30% <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/uploads/2017/07/2017y07m10d_1535462378.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F2017y07m10d_1535462378.jpg&h=abef6ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/uploads/2017/07/2017y07m10d_1535448634.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F2017y07m10d_1535448634.jpg&h=491127fd&s={SIZE}\" />劍聖套裝 暫時最型 效果強勁 好想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好難抽 唔好勉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n弓手們對唔住, 小弟暫時唔係好熟弓武, 所以請再三忍耐下等其他高手出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新手就參考下啦 高手就指教下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ae3f675e54a7a4c3f052adcc2f9856be3c8c8e","tid":609602,"uid":129852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efb8d39ef47aaade033848c3c57834c7c828920","tid":609602,"uid":129852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}